---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const locale = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us | OpenedFile"
  description="Get in touch with the OpenedFile team. Questions, feedback, bug reports, or feature requests — we'd love to hear from you."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Contact Us</h1>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a question about our tools, want to report a bug, suggest a new
          feature, or just want to say hello — don't hesitate to reach out. We value every piece of feedback and strive
          to respond to all inquiries promptly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Email</h2>
        <p>
          The best way to contact us is via email. Whether it's a technical question, business inquiry, or general
          feedback, we aim to respond within a few business days.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a
            href="mailto:contact@openedfile.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white px-6 py-4 text-gray-900 hover:border-primary-300 hover:bg-primary-50 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white dark:hover:border-primary-600 dark:hover:bg-primary-950 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2" />
              <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold">contact@openedfile.com</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">We typically respond within 1-3 business days</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What You Can Contact Us About</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/60">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3" />
                <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17" />
              </svg>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">General Questions</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Have a question about how our tools work, what formats are supported, or how your data is handled? We're
              happy to help.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/60">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-red-500 dark:text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15" />
                <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15" />
              </svg>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Bug Reports</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Found something that doesn't work correctly? Please include the file type, your browser and OS, and a
              description of the issue. Screenshots are always helpful.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/60">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 2v4" />
                <path d="m16 6-2.5 2.5" />
                <path d="M20 12h-4" />
                <path d="m16 18-2.5-2.5" />
                <path d="M12 22v-4" />
                <path d="m8 18 2.5-2.5" />
                <path d="M4 12h4" />
                <path d="m8 6 2.5 2.5" />
              </svg>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Feature Requests</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Have an idea for a new tool or an improvement to an existing one? We'd love to hear your suggestions and
              prioritize features based on user feedback.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800/60">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
                <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
                <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
              </svg>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Business Inquiries</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              Interested in partnerships, advertising, or business collaborations? We're open to hearing about
              opportunities that align with our mission.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Privacy Requests</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about our privacy practices, want to exercise your data rights (GDPR, CCPA), or need
          to report a privacy concern, please email us at
          <a href="mailto:contact@openedfile.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400">contact@openedfile.com</a>
          with "Privacy Request" in the subject line. We will respond within 30 days.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          For more details about how we handle your data, please see our
          <a href="/privacy/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Frequently Asked Before Contacting</h2>
        <p>
          Before reaching out, you might find the answer to your question on one of our tool pages. Each tool includes
          a detailed FAQ section:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 list-disc pl-6">
          <li><a href="/tools/webp/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400">WebP to JPG/PNG Converter</a> — WebP format questions, quality settings, batch conversion</li>
          <li><a href="/tools/heic/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400">HEIC to JPG/PNG Converter</a> — iPhone photo conversion, HEIC vs HEIF, quality options</li>
          <li><a href="/tools/winmail/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400">Winmail.dat Viewer</a> — TNEF format, Outlook attachments, extraction help</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Response Time</h2>
        <p>
          We aim to respond to all emails within 1 to 3 business days. During busy periods, it may take slightly longer.
          If your inquiry is urgent, please indicate this in your subject line and we will prioritize your message. Thank
          you for your patience and for choosing OpenedFile.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
